{"tid":1949891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【日本戰線】日本天王志村健武肺病逝 享壽70歲","createTime":"2020-03-30T03:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T03:32:13.000Z","uid":345002,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a5a16df2bc25c43862085506f463ecbfba2b536","tid":1949891,"uid":345002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:25:17.000Z","msg":"日本各大媒體今天快報報導志村病逝於昨晚11時10分（台灣時間昨晚10時10分）病逝於東京一家醫院。<br />\n<br />\n志村所屬經紀公司25日宣布，志村於本月20日因身體不適被送到東京一家醫院就診，經醫師診斷出罹患重度肺炎，於是住院治療。由於病情不見改善，醫師為志村進行2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）篩檢，23日晚間檢查結果出爐，呈現陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n志村於17日發病，當天出現倦怠感並在自家療養，19日有發燒、呼吸困難等症狀。20日前來他家幫他看診的醫師建議他應到醫院治療，於是被送醫。<br />\n<br />\n【日本戰線】<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nhk_news/status/1244426374707732480\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnhk_news%2Fstatus%2F1244426374707732480&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYqyNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=7a7a0194\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnhk_news%2Fstatus%2F1244426374707732480&h=93bb1e9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nhk_news/status/1244426374707732480</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aeadd272e7cc78b570fe0f6532fa323694fc23f","tid":1949891,"uid":345002,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}